com.microsoft.azure.management.network

Interface LoadBalancerOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoadBalancerOperationsImpl

    public interface LoadBalancerOperations
    The Network Resource Provider API includes operations for managing the load balancers for your subscription.
